{"tid":2240529,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天下圍中｜華大使館指導印媒遵守一中原則 印媒罕發社論回應：印度是自由國家","createTime":"2020-10-12T16:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T03:12:59.000Z","uid":240362,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b92a6df59580c8309488fb42274e3f715b8a624a","tid":2240529,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:58:15.000Z","msg":"日前中國駐印度大使館向印度傳媒發文「指導」他們報道台灣和雙十慶典時要遵守「一中原則」，引起反響。《印度斯坦時報》（Hindustan Times）周一刊出社論，提醒中國不應認為可在民主的印度向傳媒施壓，並呼籲中國改正行為。<br />\n<br />\n《印度斯坦時報》周一社論的題為「給中國的提示︰印度是自由國家」（A reminder for China: India is free），文中指出，中國駐印度大使館在「台灣國慶」前夕向多家印度傳媒發出「建議」，要求報道遵守「印度政府在台灣問題上的立場」，不能違反「一個中國」原則。此舉引起印度新聞界憤怒，印度外交部發聲明回應，強調印度傳媒可自由報道所想報道的議題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201012/63HOLLZNZZHMFHQ7WES4W7SOZM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201012%2F63HOLLZNZZHMFHQ7WES4W7SOZM%2F&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V6T%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=151be978\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201012%2F63HOLLZNZZHMFHQ7WES4W7SOZM%2F&h=329c5c63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201012/63HOLLZNZZHMFHQ7WES4W7SOZM/</a>"},{"pid":"4fa858ffdf7a088f68d4672592ff99ed90696f88","tid":2240529,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T19:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd539f652eccaa0476223bb47b57e52c64c79741","tid":2240529,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T00:31:27.000Z","msg":"面係人哋畀，架係自己丟"},{"pid":"a20fb829367fb31845b9f29d4694414e3f8d7241","tid":2240529,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T00:33:16.000Z","msg":"支那人口上戰狼"},{"pid":"3351f48c7401cb4f300f928